          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0401P0_20030313_WH_47' title='Link to this speech by Mr David Ruffley' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-david-ruffley" title="Mr David Ruffley">Mr. David Ruffley</a></cite>
          <span class='member_constituency'><a href="/constituencies/bury-st-edmunds" title="Bury St Edmunds">(Bury St. Edmunds)</a></span>
          <p class='first-para'>
            <span class="italic">rose</span>&#x2014;
          </p>
